### Curl examples for rebalancer API testing

## Health check
curl -X GET http://localhost:8000/health

## List accounts
curl -X GET http://localhost:8000/accounts

## Get account positions
curl -X GET http://localhost:8000/accounts/U20660659/positions

## Get account value
curl -X GET http://localhost:8000/accounts/U20660659/value

## Dry run rebalance (explicit endpoint)
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/rebalance/U20660659/dry-run

## Dry run rebalance (via request body)
curl -X POST \
  http://localhost:8000/rebalance/U20660659 \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{
    "execution_mode": "dry_run"
  }'

